Admin Commands <p>Modifiy Claim Chunks Count<pre><code>/ftbchunks admin extra_claim_chunks &lt;player&gt; &lt;set/add&gt; &lt;amount&gt;
</code></pre> Modify Force Loaded Chunks Count<pre><code>/ftbchunks admin extra_force_load_chunks &lt;player&gt; &lt;set/add&gt; &lt;amount&gt;
</code></pre> Bypass Chunk Claims<pre><code>/ftbchunks admin bypass_claims
</code></pre> Unload All Forced Loaded Chunks<pre><code>/ftbchunks admin unload_everything
</code></pre> Unclaim All Chunks (All Team/Player Chunks)<pre><code>/ftbchunks admin unclaim_everything
</code></pre></p>
